            <h4>Itinerary</h4>
        	<p>Friday, for our guests, we will have a welcome dinner at <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oistins">Oistins</a>, a fish market where locals and tourists gather to eat, drink, and hang out...</p><p>Saturday is the wedding. The house is in the middle of the island. We will provide transportation from your hotel to and from the wedding for our guests.</p>
<p>The bride and groom will be arriving mid-week before the wedding and will be on island through October 8th. Other than Friday and Saturday night, we'll keep the group posted about where we’ll be hanging out  so you can come meet up if you like.</p><p>Further details to come and will be posted here.</p>
          
